display_long_description:
# Welcome to the MasterRunners Page.

MasterRunners is a free-to-play, hand-based movement VR multiplayer game packed with fun and variety. It offers a one-of-a-kind experience that stands out in the VR space. Whether you're into fast-paced action or just looking to hang out with friends, MasterRunners has something for everyone.

# What you can do:
- Play Gamemodes with players across the **WORLD**. MasterRunners can be played worldwide and with our **advanced multiplayer system**, you can enjoy multiplayer & have a very fun time. For the gamemodes, we build special gamemodes that have never been used in others games making us stand out and more fun.
[media]
- Chill with friends and have a **great time.** With areas such as the "Main Hub", you can relax and have a calming time with buddies as you talk to your hearts desire.
[media]
- Shop for new cosmetics at the Master Mart with the in-game currency... Energy! Using energy, you can get all kinds of cosmetics of any type just with one click. This is how you can customize your character!
[media]

And more. 

There is lots to do in MasterRunners, so check it out **TODAY!**
[media]
